article_id:1995,category_name:News,title_name:Announcing the Next Summon Showcase: Dragon Special!,image_path:,message:<div>The next Summon Showcase: Dragon Special kicks off <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1613973600"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>The appearance rates for featured 4★ and 5★ dragons will be boosted.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured dragons:</div><div>■Dragons</div><div>5★ Giovanni (shadow)</div><div>5★ Apollo (flame)</div><div>5★ Andromeda (shadow)</div><div>4★ Phoenix (flame)</div><div>4★ Ifrit (flame)</div><div>4★ Juggernaut (shadow)</div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for the Dragon Special showcase:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1613973600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1614319199"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the featured dragons below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured dragons:</div><div>
