				<div class="param">
					<ul>
						<li>A dragon captured by the vile Syndicate.<br>She shoulders the sins of all people, and through<br>offering herself up cleanses them of said sin.<br>...Or so it is said; she lost her memory due to<br>Syndicate testing, and now travels with Aldred.</li>
